ms of the disparity. Evaluating existing programs through rigorous data collection and analysis can help identify effective strategies while discarding those that fall short. Ultimately, closing the gender gap in science requires sustained commitment across all levels of scientific endeavor to cultivate an environment where talent is nurtured irrespective of gender."
